pay anything off, okay?

00:57:16.320 --> 00:57:20.410
So the key is about matching
and then capacitating.

00:57:20.410 --> 00:57:22.500
Matching and then capacitating.

00:57:22.500 --> 00:57:26.110
Now, if we do that, starting in
this country, and then we do it

00:57:26.110 --> 00:57:33.360
